&lt;p&gt;Thank you very much for the quick review and happy weekend &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/smile.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17357665" author="edimitrova" created="Fri, 4 Jun 2021 22:55:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;New ticket was opened to facilitate the fix of the issue in Cassandra 3.11 -&#160;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-16714&quot; title=&quot;Fix org.apache.cassandra.utils.SlidingTimeRateTest.testConcurrentUpdateAndGet&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-16714&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-16714&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
